title: Kodiak J-250 48 in. Round Point Shovel with Fiberglass Handle and Serrated Blade
description: 48 in. heavy-duty contractor-grade fiberglass handle is stronger than wood. Large steel collar for added strength. Extra-thick 14-gauge steel blade for maximum toughness. Serrated blade for easy soil penetration. Dual diameter grip inside poly sleeve provides barrier between handle and grip. Outside, soft-cushioned grip provides added comfort and control. Safety sleeve helps prevent splintering.
